content.description: Loads from Metal staging layer to the Bronze tables. SCD2(maintains history of the records, active records are open ended and old ones have closed date)
content.name: cdi_map_adm_agency_license_bronze_load

object.customQuery:
with current_batch as (
select
	bls.batch_id,
	bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
	bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
from
	$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
where
	bls.source_system_code ='$$sourcesystemcode'
	and bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	and bls.batch_id = (
	select
		MAX(batch_id)
	from
		$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
	where
		source_system_code ='$$sourcesystemcode'
		and batch_status = 'Inprogress' ) )
select
	distinct
	metal_aal.source_name,
	metal_aal.load_type,
	metal_aal.agency_id,
	metal_aal.bs_appointed_date,
	metal_aal.ca_appointed_date,
	metal_aal.created,
	metal_aal.delete_flag,
	metal_aal.expiration_date,
	metal_aal.id,
	metal_aal.license_number,
	metal_aal.lob,
	metal_aal.mk_appointed_date,
	metal_aal.modified,
	metal_aal.state,
	metal_aal.term_id,
       metal_aal.license_class,
       current_batch.batch_id
from
	$$raw_schema.adm_agency_license metal_aal
cross join current_batch
order by
	metal_aal.id,
	metal_aal.created,
	metal_aal.modified;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

object.customQuery:
select
	adm_agency_license_row_id,
	adm_agency_license_batch_id,
	adm_agency_license_row_md5checksum,
        id,
	modified,
	adm_agency_license_row_effective_end_datetime
from
	$$staging_schema.adm_agency_license
where
	adm_agency_license_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
